TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
Select FISCAL_YEAR as FISCAL_YEAR, FISCAL_PERIOD as FISCAL_PERIOD, COMP_CODE as COMP_CODE, MEASURE as MEASURE, SUM(SALES$) AS SALES$ FROM ( SELECT FISCAL_YEAR AS FISCAL_YEAR, FISCAL_PERIOD AS FISCAL_PERIOD, Substr(TRIM(GL_ACCT_NUM_1),1,4) as COMP_CODE, SALES_MEASURE_NAME AS MEASURE, SUM(DOLLARS) AS SALES$ FROM GROSS_MARGIN,(select case when d.cy_month_num ='1' then to_char(to_number(cy_year_yyyy) -1) else cy_year_yyyy end || case when d.cy_month_num ='1' then '12' else to_char(to_number(d.cy_month_num)-1) end prevyrpd from slba.day_dimension d where day_date = trunc(sysdate)) DAY_DIM WHERE SLBA_DIVISION_CODE='SC' AND UPDATE_USERID NOT LIKE '%SAP%' AND TO_CHAR(FISCAL_YEAR||FISCAL_PERIOD) = DAY_DIM.PREVYRPD AND DOLLARS <>0 AND GROSS_MARGIN_IND='Y' GROUP BY FISCAL_YEAR,FISCAL_PERIOD,Substr(TRIM(GL_ACCT_NUM_1),1,4),SALES_MEASURE_NAME
UNION ALL SELECT FISCAL_YEAR AS FISCAL_YEAR, FISCAL_PERIOD AS FISCAL_PERIOD, Substr(TRIM(GL_ACCT_NUM_2),1,4) as COMP_CODE, COST_MEASURE_NAME AS MEASURE, SUM(adj_extended_cost_dollars) AS SALES$ FROM GROSS_MARGIN,( SELECT case when d.cy_month_num ='1' then to_char(to_number(cy_year_yyyy) -1) else cy_year_yyyy end || case when d.cy_month_num ='1' then '12' else to_char(to_number(d.cy_month_num)-1) end prevyrpd from slba.day_dimension d where day_date = trunc(sysdate)) DAY_DIM WHERE SLBA_DIVISION_CODE='SC' AND UPDATE_USERID NOT LIKE '%SAP%' AND TO_CHAR(FISCAL_YEAR||FISCAL_PERIOD) = DAY_DIM.PREVYRPD AND ADJ_EXTENDED_COST_DOLLARS <>0 AND GROSS_MARGIN_IND='Y' GROUP BY FISCAL_YEAR,FISCAL_PERIOD,Substr(TRIM(GL_ACCT_NUM_2),1,4),COST_MEASURE_NAME ) GROUP BY FISCAL_YEAR,FISCAL_PERIOD,COMP_CODE,MEASURE ORDER BY FISCAL_YEAR,FISCAL_PERIOD,COMP_CODE,MEASURE --

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: FISCAL_YEAR = I_FISCAL_YEAR AND FISCAL_PERIOD = I_FISCAL_PERIOD AND COMP_CODE = I_COMPANY AND MEASURE = I_MEASURE_NAME

When the input recordset has the Gross OS record with an amount < 10 million, the flag is set to 0 (in the EXP_MEASURE_NAME). Hence in this aggregator we determine the min of threshold value always.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: AGG_THRESHOLD_MIN

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION:
Source Qualifier to join DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS and DW_GL_ACCOUNT.
4/7/2009 - Bug fix - If the Gross OS record (after SAMBA GL XREF lookup) is present with amount < 10,000,000, records for that year and period should not load. This threshold condition failed when the source did not have a Gross OS record at all. The "union all" will now include the Gross OS record (min gl account is 4100000000) with amount of 0 when the source does not have a Gross OS record. Retain this condition for the threshold to function correctly. Also included the convert function for the post_date, as max is being performed on character datatype, it should be date datatype.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_SUM_DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT FISCAL_YEAR AS FISCAL_YEAR, PERIOD AS PERIOD, Company as COMPANY, YEARPD AS YEARPD, ACCOUNT AS ACCOUNT, CONVERT(VARCHAR(20),MAX(POST_DATE)) AS POST_DATE, SUM(AMOUNT_ESS) AS AMOUNT_ESS
FROM ( SELECT DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS.Fiscal_Year, DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS.Period, case when substring(cast(DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS.Company as varchar),1,3) in ('348','349') then '3450' else cast(DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS.Company as varchar) end as company, ltrim(rtrim(cast(DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS.Fiscal_Year as char(4)))) +ltrim(rtrim(cast(DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS.Period as char(2)))) as YEARPD, (DW_GL_ACCOUNT.Account+DW_GL_ACCOUNT.SUB_Account) AS ACCOUNT, MAX(CONVERT(DATETIME, DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS.Post_Date, 121)) AS Post_Date, SUM(DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS.Amount_Ess) AS Amount_Ess FROM DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS with(NOLOCK), DW_GL_ACCOUNT with(NOLOCK) WHERE DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS.Acct_Key=DW_GL_ACCOUNT.Acct_Key AND DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS.Currency_Type='BASE' AND DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS.Company_Group='SLSC GRP' AND DW_GL_ACCOUNT.Chart_Section='Income Statement' AND substring(DW_GL_ACCOUNT.Account,1,3)<>'425' AND DW_GL_ACCOUNT.ACCOUNT NOT IN('510053') AND DW_GL_ACCOUNT.ACCOUNT < '600000' AND DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS.Fiscal_Year in (cast(substring(cast(getdate() as char(50)),8,4) as int), cast(substring(cast(getdate() as char(50)),8,4) as int)-1) GROUP BY DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS.Fiscal_Year, DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS.Period, DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS.Company, (DW_GL_ACCOUNT.Account+DW_GL_ACCOUNT.SUB_Account)
UNION ALL SELECT DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS.Fiscal_Year AS Fiscal_Year , DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS.Period AS Period, '000' as company, ltrim(rtrim(cast(DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS.Fiscal_Year as char(4))))+ltrim(rtrim(cast(DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS.Period as char(2)))) as YEARPD, '4100000000' AS ACCOUNT, MAX(CONVERT(DATETIME, DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS.Post_Date, 121)) AS Post_Date, 0 AS Amount_Ess FROM DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS with(NOLOCK), DW_GL_ACCOUNT with(NOLOCK) WHERE DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS.Acct_Key=DW_GL_ACCOUNT.Acct_Key AND DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS.Currency_Type='BASE' AND DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS.Company_Group='SLSC GRP' AND DW_GL_ACCOUNT.Chart_Section='Income Statement' AND substring(DW_GL_ACCOUNT.Account,1,3)<>'425' AND DW_GL_ACCOUNT.ACCOUNT NOT IN('510053') AND DW_GL_ACCOUNT.ACCOUNT < '600000' AND DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS.Fiscal_Year in (cast(substring(cast(getdate() as char(50)),8,4) as int), cast(substring(cast(getdate() as char(50)),8,4) as int)-1) GROUP BY DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS.Fiscal_Year, DW_GL_TRANSACTIONS.Period ) TXN
GROUP BY FISCAL_YEAR, PERIOD, Company, YEARPD, ACCOUNT ORDER BY FISCAL_YEAR, PERIOD, ACCOUNT

SESSION.NAME: s_m_GROSS_MARGIN_SC_LAWSON_HIST

ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Pre SQL
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE: delete from gross_margin where slba_division_code='SC' and update_userid='SCLawsonETL' and (fiscal_year=(SELECT CY_YEAR_YYYY FROM DAY_DIMENSION WHERE DAY_DIMENSION.DAY_DATE=TRUNC(SYSDATE)) OR fiscal_year =(SELECT CY_YEAR_YYYY-1 FROM DAY_DIMENSION WHERE DAY_DIMENSION.DAY_DATE=TRUNC(SYSDATE)))

ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE: Select FISCAL_YEAR as FISCAL_YEAR, FISCAL_PERIOD as FISCAL_PERIOD, COMP_CODE as COMP_CODE, MEASURE as MEASURE, SUM(SALES$) AS SALES$ FROM ( SELECT FISCAL_YEAR AS FISCAL_YEAR, FISCAL_PERIOD AS FISCAL_PERIOD, SUBSTR(TRIM(GL_ACCT_NUM_1),1,4) as COMP_CODE, SALES_MEASURE_NAME AS MEASURE, SUM(DOLLARS) AS SALES$ FROM GROSS_MARGIN,(select distinct cy_year_yyyy||cy_month_num as YEARPD from slba.day_dimension d where cy_year_yyyy in(SELECT CY_YEAR_YYYY FROM DAY_DIMENSION WHERE DAY_DIMENSION.DAY_DATE=TRUNC(SYSDATE)) OR cy_year_yyyy =(SELECT CY_YEAR_YYYY-1 FROM DAY_DIMENSION WHERE DAY_DIMENSION.DAY_DATE=TRUNC(SYSDATE))) DAY_DIM WHERE SLBA_DIVISION_CODE='SC' AND UPDATE_USERID NOT LIKE '%SAP%' AND TO_CHAR(FISCAL_YEAR||FISCAL_PERIOD) = DAY_DIM.YEARPD AND DOLLARS <>0 AND GROSS_MARGIN_IND='Y' GROUP BY FISCAL_YEAR,FISCAL_PERIOD,SUBSTR(TRIM(GL_ACCT_NUM_1),1,4) ,SALES_MEASURE_NAME UNION ALL SELECT FISCAL_YEAR AS FISCAL_YEAR, FISCAL_PERIOD AS FISCAL_PERIOD, SUBSTR(TRIM(GL_ACCT_NUM_2),1,4) as COMP_CODE, CASE WHEN ( FISCAL_YEAR < 2008 OR ( FISCAL_YEAR = 2008 AND FISCAL_PERIOD <= 7) ) THEN DECODE(COST_MEASURE_NAME, 'IC COGS', 'OS COGS', COST_MEASURE_NAME) ELSE COST_MEASURE_NAME END MEASURE, SUM(adj_extended_cost_dollars) AS SALES$ FROM GROSS_MARGIN,(select distinct cy_year_yyyy||cy_month_num as YEARPD from slba.day_dimension d where cy_year_yyyy in(SELECT CY_YEAR_YYYY FROM DAY_DIMENSION WHERE DAY_DIMENSION.DAY_DATE=TRUNC(SYSDATE)) OR cy_year_yyyy =(SELECT CY_YEAR_YYYY-1 FROM DAY_DIMENSION WHERE DAY_DIMENSION.DAY_DATE=TRUNC(SYSDATE))) DAY_DIM WHERE SLBA_DIVISION_CODE='SC' AND UPDATE_USERID NOT LIKE '%SAP%' AND TO_CHAR(FISCAL_YEAR||FISCAL_PERIOD) = DAY_DIM.YEARPD AND ADJ_EXTENDED_COST_DOLLARS <>0 AND GROSS_MARGIN_IND='Y' GROUP BY FISCAL_YEAR,FISCAL_PERIOD,SUBSTR(TRIM(GL_ACCT_NUM_2),1,4), CASE WHEN ( FISCAL_YEAR < 2008 OR ( FISCAL_YEAR = 2008 AND FISCAL_PERIOD <= 7) ) THEN DECODE(COST_MEASURE_NAME, 'IC COGS', 'OS COGS', COST_MEASURE_NAME) ELSE COST_MEASURE_NAME END ) GROUP BY FISCAL_YEAR,FISCAL_PERIOD,COMP_CODE, MEASURE ORDER BY FISCAL_YEAR,FISCAL_PERIOD,COMP_CODE, MEASURE --

ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select distinct cy_year_yyyy||cy_month_num as YEARPD from slba.day_dimension d where cy_year_yyyy in (Select to_number(cy_year_yyyy) from day_dimension where Trunc(day_date) = Trunc(Sysdate)) or cy_year_yyyy in(Select to_number(cy_year_yyyy)-1 from day_dimension where Trunc(day_date) = Trunc(Sysdate))
